4) Notice that mt_ckd_h2o_module.f90 does
    rho_rat = (p_atm/dat%ref_press)*(dat%ref_temp/t_atm)
    sh2o_coeff = sh2o_coeff * h2o_vmr * rho_rat
    fh2o_coeff = fh2o_coeff * (1-h2o_vmr) * rho_rat
    if (radflag) then
      sh2o_coeff(v) = sh2o_coeff(v) * radfn(v,T)
      fh2o_coeff(v) = fh2o_coeff(v) * radfn(v,T)      
    end
    where radfn(v,T) = c2/T * v * (1-exp(v2v/2T))/(1.+exp(c2v/2T))    
  and passes these back to cntnm_progr_sergio.f90
  
  So that means cntnm_progr_sergio.f90 has to do
    rho_rat = (p_atm/1013.00) * (296/t_atm);
    sh2o = sh2o/(rho_rat * h2o_frac)
    fh2o = fh2o/(rho_rat * (1-h2o_frac))
  before it does
    raAbs(I)  = gamma_T*(rXSelf*sh2o(I)*ppaveIN + rXforn*fh2o(I)*(paveIN-ppaveIN))   where gamma_T = 1
    
  Then do_local_lineshape_CKD.m either does
    raAbs = raAbs (if you are looking for total OD)
  or
    raAbs = raAbs/radfn(v,T)/raPP        for self continuum coeff
    raAbs = raAbs/radfn(v,T)/(raP-raPP)  for forn continuum coeff
     
